	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">De servo pistoris <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l546" cert="high">Wiennae</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2560" cert="high">Austrię</placeName> combusto haec habeo: Nosti, quomodo sacerdoti</foreign> er hat das sacrament mit der monstrantzen genomen an unsers herte/rregots tag uß den henden, das mit fuͤssen getretten zuͦ stucken.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de">Den haben sy gefangen ein lange zit, haben in wellen bereden</foreign> se peccasse in spiritum sanctum, et si vellet revocare suum erratum et dicere se a Zwinglianis seductum, tunc mitem sententiam habiturum.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod noluit et perpetuo dixit idololatriam esse crudelissimam, propter quam <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18593">Turcam</persName> dominus immiserit tandem adductus ad iudicem et 1. lingua illi praecisa, ne loqueretur ad populum, 2. manus ambas amputatę, 3. igne combustus est.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Constantissimus fuit et perpetuo in populum oculos suos direxit; multos commovit ad lachrymas profundendas.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Paffi triumphant.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dixit martyr ad iudices: "Si deus fuit, cur se non defendit, cur me non fulmine perdidit?</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habebitis brevi alios, qui vestram superstitionem reprehendent, si illos non audieritis, <persName ref="p18593" cert="high">Turcę</persName> servi eritis."</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc de pistore.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> nihil omnino audimus, et quidam heri ad nos venit, qui ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808" cert="high">Belgis</placeName> rediit, de <persName ref="p18538" cert="high">Cęsaris</persName> infirmitate varia narrans.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ducis captu filius natu maior in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l825" cert="high">Dania</placeName> est, regem fortassis sollicitaturus, an posset liberare parentem e captivitate illa Caesareana.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749">Saxonicę</placeName> civitates adhuc se fortiter defendunt contra quorundam nebulonum tyrannides.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <placeName type="auto_name">Brunswicensi</placeName> proditione audisti absque dubio.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vigilandum est civitatibus, ne per istas insidias adobruantur.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">15. ianuarii 1550.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodorum</persName> salutabis, <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicanum</persName>, <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvaltherum</persName> et praecipue <persName ref="p1214" cert="high">Frisium</persName> nostrum.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto ad te bullam diaboli; nam papa mortuus est, qui hasce... bullas dedit vanissimas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quum clauderem literas, ad me mittuntur ex <placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> hęc tristia: <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4744">Fagius</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l86" cert="high">Cantabrigiae</placeName> ex quartana diutina eaque quasi in tabem desinente ad cęlestem patriam die 23. novembris concessit.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name">Latamerus</persName> episcopus laetaliter decumbit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerus</persName> recte valet, si modo is fidelissimi collegae et exulis morte potest dici recte valere.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc fusius audies brevi absque dubio ipso d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8121">Montio</persName>, qui literas ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> accepit iis diebus, quę et tibi communicabit<note type="margin">a.R.: scheint eher "tu communicabis".</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Doctissimo ac piissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinę</placeName> ecclesiae pastori vigilantissimo, domino suo perpetuo venerando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
